{"tid":232862,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"fyp番2 個月時間做， machine learning","createTime":"2017-05-07T06:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T13:20:03.000Z","uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc03349347e8820c316f16a6217d1ddd0792bf6","tid":232862,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"應該會比人串我做咩搞到咁少時間先開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我係有苦葱<br />\n<br />\n想問我想做個類似predict樓價既網<br />\n我本身識寫front end back end<br />\n<br />\n但對machine learb得好少知識，<br />\n而家連data都未有<br />\n<br />\n有人指點下小兄點樣開波最快？<br />\n我成日糾結於用邊隻演算法先岩。。<br />\n<br />\n利申： 諗著用scikitlearn粗粗地用著先<br />\n利申2: 數底差"},{"pid":"b8298702788c66481268e49501544e131eaef14a","tid":232862,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，咁多種predictive learning 入面，搞economy market 係幾花時間，兩個月不如轉topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117989b5367f4a587268a7141609ec3cb175b765","tid":232862,"uid":23495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"苦葱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17618f3221fd6a4e059d54d13a20835f403d0f4","tid":232862,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"數底差既我當年FYP係學點用UNREAL ENGINE同埋嘗試下做Game Engine Programmer<br />\n不過身邊總有班廢人數底仲廢過你，又好有自信地覺得由盤古初開寫到UNREAL ENGINE出黎，就算係以前AL/CE A撚晒個班人係寫唔撚到<br />\n我講左啲咩自己參透下啦"},{"pid":"858cfd5e1bf44e5e79cd68dc811783b1e9f92ab7","tid":232862,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"問返professor"},{"pid":"9c980f3e4d6a769465dc963b74f39be53f91a44b","tid":232862,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:22:23.000Z","msg":"比錢買"},{"pid":"3af9892d972dc43aae9fc7c327313bf78c5aed69","tid":232862,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"乜都唔識仲想2個月搞掂 收皮啦"},{"pid":"57ce10ac59e259bd16b9a0b22d5732ae6b34c32d","tid":232862,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02b452ffd8ad2c75a173fcb55a5680653776c30d","tid":232862,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"原先計劃係睇<br />\nsentdex d machine learning教學<br />\n<br />\n知道左supervise unsupervised分別<br />\ndecision tree哩 d岩唔岩用哩個case?<br />\n有 d人就話用random forest,  gradient boosting( 哩個好似多stat野wo)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個fyp實則時間得3 個幾月<br />\n而家得番 2 個月左右時間<br />\n<br />\n中途又因為身體出左意外<br />\n時間浪費左<br />\n之前就學python d sybtax<br />\n而家諗返根本唔洗學d syntax而應該直接黎料"},{"pid":"b4d5fe28ee46b209d3cfa97a95e3363780a588cc","tid":232862,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"聽大家咁講<br />\n好似2個月時間真係唔夠做咁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f01360d669bd4936c9749c1f6c980442f1e8257","tid":232862,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老豆豆，咁多種predictive learning 入面，搞economy market 係幾花時間，兩個月不如轉topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原先就係想挑戰自己<br />\n用3 個半月搞ml<br />\n同professor申請轉topuic做 ml<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf87b780536f88d110a76a496c2e3bc11adcec9","tid":232862,"uid":51741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:12:53.000Z","msg":"你個FYP偏向theory定偏向整product,如果偏向做product ，其實你識front end back end 加sklearn 可以好快做完睇落有d料到既網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0823fc7fb625f6e67ddd13e9bcae63ff72fb598","tid":232862,"uid":15072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"你係想predict exact value 定movement? exact value 好難做高accuracy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我FYP個陣用support vector machine 做你類似既野"},{"pid":"8049433fa244be51f236d1dc07b8930f94d265f4","tid":232862,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"算吧啦, 轉topic啦, <br />\n<br />\n你唔識ml又要design又要有product demo, 你一定唔會夠時間"},{"pid":"c382dcf6b24e923f51d15fce9d032d5ba87d8b90","tid":232862,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"小弟做過<br />\n好易做"},{"pid":"7ed1ae48921fb846a8d6f976c0b80b1a84acac50","tid":232862,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"Kaggle 有幾個 competition 同 real estate pricing 有關，你可以去望望<br />\n<br />\n你有 historic data 可以做 supervised learning<br />\n揀啱 label 搞好 feature 就可以做 prediction<br />\n<br />\n上邊有巴絲講過估方向會易過實質數值<br />\n估方向係 two-class classification<br />\n實質數值要 regression 會難啲準<br />\n<br />\n之後有乜詳細可以再一齊研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8484e68e38d1b49364f8ecf04bfc17206707b2","tid":232862,"uid":74254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"defer半年囉, 無咩大不了"},{"pid":"1842e7094163c5347c1cb9af2b207262f1f47a83","tid":232862,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nretake罷啦"},{"pid":"374dbeb0ae1298acff8a5102c6117ab1a25314ab","tid":232862,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"一個個星期都做到demo 啦"},{"pid":"66d08ed7b164a6d4b634541732440b1b5145ffc3","tid":232862,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"兩個月都應該起到貨大家點解咁嚇樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"